{"tid":1537003,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"俾人嫌棄得多，反而放開左","createTime":"2019-09-03T18:50:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T18:50:59.000Z","uid":58316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a7510317fa55b5e1a1d8043709b1273f4b012940","tid":1537003,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:50:48.000Z","msg":"討好人<br />\n又係俾人嫌棄<br />\n自把自為<br />\n又係俾人嫌棄<br />\n可能你會覺得<br />\n你當自己咩<br />\n係你適應社會<br />\n唔係掉返轉<br />\n所以而家<br />\n唔反抗亦唔接受<br />\n不置可否<br />\n自己ok就算<br />\n我講呢d野<br />\n唔會聲大大<br />\n話自己幾慘<br />\n幾唔忿氣<br />\n因為我知道<br />\n一熄左部電腦<br />\n一出左門口<br />\n落到街<br />\n我就咩都唔係<br />\n上黎講<br />\n只係一種生理需要<br />\n唔講就屈死<br />\n我呢世人<br />\n除左呢少少空間<br />\n仲有咩係我自己<br />\n出面係點一件事<br />\n自己感受一件事<br />\n自己既感受<br />\n自己感受就夠<br />\n有d野<br />\n我好想話唔係<br />\n但一到呢d時候<br />\n夜晚攝高枕頭<br />\n就露哂底<br />\n我未至於悲哀到<br />\n甘心呃埋自己"},{"pid":"cefede8441536b9179e4fa9fc867b35a5e36f86f","tid":1537003,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:50:59.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt